              "plain_text": "Heterogenous Information network embedding-based Recommendations face challenges related with the heterogenous nature of the way users or items are represented. The authors propose a new form of recommendations SEMH4Rec that is meant to create better representations of users and items and feeds them to a Matrix Factorization algorithm.",
